Train your respiratory system. Stress management techniques include breathing exercises. 
This particular breathing exercise is a great place to start mindful breathing techniques.

Box Breathing

1. Imagine a box or a square
2. Inhale as you count to 4 - that's the first wall of the box
3. Keep the breath as you count to 4 - that's the second wall of the box
4. Exhale as you count to 4 - that's the third wall of the box
5. Keep the breath as you count to 4 - that's the fourth wall of the box 

Repeat this exercise twice as day - morning and evening - 60 counts - build 60 walls.
